      <title>Uber 作为投资级公司启动首次债券发售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/uber-kicks-off-its-first-bond-sale-as-investment-grade-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司 (Uber Technologies Inc.) 自获得蓝筹股地位以来首次进入美国投资级债券市场。]]></description>
